(24370, 'Oxaleptal 300 mg 30 f.c.tabs.', 'اوكساليبتال 300مجم 30 قرص', '136.5', '180', 'Oxcarbazepine', 'Mash premiere', 'Tab', 'أقراص', 'علاج الصرع -- تقليل التشنجات', 'Anti-epileptic.carboxamides', '300 mg', 'In the United States, oxcarbazepine is indicated for use as monotherapy or adjunctive therapy in the treatment of partial-onset seizures in adults and as monotherapy in the treatment of partial-onset seizures in pediatric patients aged 4 years and above, and as adjunctive therapy in pediatric patients aged 2 years and above with partial-onset seizures.[L8627] 
In Canada, oxcarbazepine is indicated for use as monotherapy or adjunctive therapy in the treatment of partial-onset seizures in patients 6 years of age and older.[L8630]', '6222001400458', '', 7030, '2024-08-03', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
(18959, 'Fentex mouth spray 60 ml', 'فنتكس سبراي للفم 60 مل', '50', '70', 'Clove oil+tea tree oil+chamomile oil+sage ext+thyme oil+menthol crystals', 'Leader > pharmacia elite', 'Spray', 'بخاخ', 'سبراي مطهر للفم', 'Antiseptic mouth spray', '60 ml', 'Clove oil is primarily indicated in conditions like colic, flatulence, and toothache [L2849].', '6224000301705', '', 6254, '2025-11-21', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
