(27847, 'T4-thyro 50 mcg 100 tabs.', 'تي4-ثيرو 50مكجم 100 قرص', '41', '46', 'Levothyroxine', 'Mup', 'Tab', 'أقراص', 'علاج قصور الغدة الدرقية', 'Thyroid hormone', '50 mcg', 'Levothyroxine is indicated as replacement therapy in primary (thyroidal), secondary (pituitary) and tertiary (hypothalamic) congenital or acquired hypothyroidism. It is also indicated as an adjunct to surgery and radioiodine therapy in the management of thyrotropin-dependent well-differentiated thyroid cancer.', '6221508522717', '', 2196, '2025-05-31', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
